<p><font style="font-size: 300%; color: maroon;">Why Consider<br>Our Programs for Your Career</font>
<img src="https://855599.smushcdn.com/1848641/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/admission-doctoral-program.jpg?lossy=1&strip=1&webp=1" alt="Error loading image" 
height="280" width="500" align="right"><br><br><br><font style="font-size: 200%; font-family: sans-serif;">The School of Computer Science & Engineering is a unique school that leverages the high-quality programs of Xavier University and emphasizes sound computer science fundamentals, coding, research, innovation, and entrepreneurship. It currently offers B.Tech. in Computer Science & Engineering, M. Tech in Data Science & Analytics, and Ph.D in Computer Science and Engineering.</font>
</p>
